
## OUTSIDE MIRROR GLASS INSTALLATION  


1. Put on gloves and safety glasses. 
2. Insert the bottom of the mirror glass holder with the mirror glass into the frame to install the lower clips (1). 
3. Press the top of the mirror glass holder with the mirror glass onto the frame to install the upper clips (2).  

